===Noun===
'''NAND'''
#A [[binary]] [[operator]] [[composite]] of [[NOT]] [[AND]]; [[negation]] of AND function.

(0 NAND 0) = 1<br>
(0 NAND 1) = 1<br>
(1 NAND 0) = 1<br>
(1 NAND 1) = 0<br>

